{
  "chapter": 14,
  "chapter_summary": "辛捷与菁儿海难后流落小戢岛，遇世外三仙之首平凡上人。平凡上人赠仙果助辛捷恢复功力，并以醍醐灌顶之法传授二十年功力。辛捷施展七妙神君剑法，与平凡上人拆招，展现虬枝剑式精妙。慧大师现身，揭示归元四象阵之名，平凡上人十年未破阵。辛捷参悟阵法要诀，欲助平凡上人破阵。本章揭示辛捷功力大幅提升，剑法精进，并引入世外三仙的赌斗恩怨。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小娃儿，听够了么？还不与我下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "吃点东西吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我这仙果非同凡品，看你步履凝稳，倒像是有几十年内功在身一样，你用功运气一番就知道这果子的好处了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "谢谢老前辈厚赐，晚辈受益匪浅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿现在才知道好处吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿，你的内功可真不错呵，看你运功情形不会是无极岛主的门人，更不是小戢岛的路子，难道除了我们三个老不死的，天下还有其他如此精奥的功夫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈辛捷拜见平凡上人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈这点末学哪能与世外三仙相提并论。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "老者",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小小年纪就言不由衷，我知你心中定自以为你师傅功夫能胜过世外三仙是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈确是由衷之言，方才晚辈一生所学连无恨生的一招都接不下……唉……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你和无恨生交过手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "前辈你——",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "且不问你师承，我倒要问你，那无恨生点你时是否使的是'拂穴'手法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "以你的功力无论如何不致一招就逃不出去，想来你必是太过紧张，才被无恨生一招得手的。我原先还以为无恨生这家伙十年不见功力竟精进如斯，原来他还是'拂穴'这手老功夫。哈哈，他这'拂穴'虽是不凡，却也算不上什么真正绝妙的功夫。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃儿你可知道老衲的年岁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "便是老衲自己也记不清楚了，总之大约二十多年前无恨生他们曾以此筝赠我，说是祝老衲三甲子大寿——呵，这筝竟给我打毁了——倒也算得上——件上古珍品呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "无恨生不过仗着一颗仙果而已，否则凭他那点功力，岂能名列世外三仙？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "四十多年前，咱们世外三仙在无极岛上互相印证功夫，无恨生仗仙果之功，驻颜不老方面自然胜过老衲，但论到真实功力，那无恨生也自认钦服老衲的，却只有这小戢岛主慧大师，不肯认输，想我老衲这么大年纪了还会和她真正动手？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你老弟年纪轻轻，功力却如此之纯，实在难得，想不到中原还有如此人物能调教出你这样的人才。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你以为输给无恨生就自认功夫太差吗？其实你忘了一件最重要的事；，",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈忘了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你可忘了\"功力\"两字，无恨生曾服仙果，再加上近百年修炼，岂是你二十几岁娃娃可能敌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你看这石头怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这你可信得过老衲的话了吧！老实说，你别把无恨生看得那么高，我老和尚不用传你一招半式，只要略为成全你，以你的本门招式，与他接个百来招，保管没有问题。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你胆敢不信老衲所言？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "老前辈虽然功力盖世，无奈晚辈功力与人家相差太远，自知绝不可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "此话当真？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈确信如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好，咱们赌上一赌，你且过来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡大师",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "现你可再运功一周后，对这石笋发一掌试试。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "娃娃你莫谢我，就是老衲也从你运功时得到不少内功妙诀，哈哈，你那师父果是一代奇人，要知虽是以我的功力打入你穴道内，但如你本身没有一种精妙与老衲内功相当的内力引导，也是徒然，现在你总该相信你本门内功精妙不在无恨生之下了吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "由你的内功上猜想，你师门的拳剑功夫必亦精奇，你且施一两招给我老儿看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "若我施一招'吴刚伐桂'，你怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我用一招'横飞渡江'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "老尼",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "老和尚变相授徒，大概是怕一身功夫葬送此阵，想找衣钵传人是不是？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "还剩一个时辰了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆休得猖狂，还有一个时辰呢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "贫尼略布小阵就令你十年无法破解，还有你说口的份么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "text": "老尼婆且不要得意，惹得老衲性起，就拼了一甲子功力也让你这小岛陆沉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hui_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "慧大师",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "告诉你也不妨，这阵乃是唤着'归元四象阵'，你若把它当'奇门五行阵'，那就大大错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "平凡上人",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "喂，娃儿，你赶快设法离开这岛，半个时辰内，愈远愈好，咦？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "老前辈且慢——",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhe",
      "text": "晚辈总算将这‘归元四象阵’的要诀记了起来——",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 14,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    }
  ],
